FoxFingers watches the action as it unfolds he sees Dinobot on the 
ground and Prowl trying to help him . It brought back memories of his 
life before he met Veratis and LadyHawk. A life he'd never know 
again. He figured that someone else would be better suited to move 
Hot Rod so he scampered in the direction of Prowl. "Is your friene 
functioning?" He yelled at the top of his vocal unit as he ran to 
help.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> You missed the small but important fact that Prowl is kinda flying 
40 feet or 
> so up in the air, Carnage, but we can say he was on the ground.
> 
> ::Oblitertron/Prowl::
> 
> Prowl's eyes widen as he sees the Oblitercons combine. That was the 
one thing 
> he hadn't wanted to happen; the giant Alliance gestalt caused too 
much death 
> and destruction.
> 
> A shadow covers Prowl as Dinobot runs up to him, mechfluid spraying 
over 
> Prowl as Dinobot is hit. He swears, glancing back at Oblitertron as 
another 
> shadow passes over him, this one of Oblitertron's foot.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Oblitertron laughs as Dinobot is hit with his optic lasers, 
bringing a foot 
> down on the two bots. Before the foot has a chance to hit either of 
them, 
> though, a tail smashes into Oblitertron's head, the bot stubling to 
the side, 
> his foot missing the Maximals by a few feet.
> 
> He spins around, firing his rifle and optic lasers at Necromancer.
